The,Placecast,Match,API,is,a,free,tool,that,enables,location,content,providers,and,location,based,application,developers,to,refer,to,a,location,in,any,number,of,ways,and,validate,that,those,references,resolve,to,one,true,location,on,the,planet,The,Placecast,Match,API,aims,to,be,transparent,and,neutral,and,allows,everyone,to,talk,to,everyone,in,the,location,based,LBS,ecosystem